name: The Wilcox Stool
description: With its elegant profile, the expertly crafted Wilcox is a unique piece with a distinct aesthetic and character all its own. A generous and stately seat sits above the sweeping lines of the Wilcox's legs, creating a masterful piece of luxury furniture that brings both comfort and charisma to a room. An eye-catching frame with its alluring silhouette, the Wilcox can be finished in any of DAVIDSON's luxury timbers and upholstered in a fabric or leather of your choice to perfectly suit any interior.
